A woman has been arrested for allegedly kidnapping a baby boy in Cheptais, Mt Elgon. Neighbours who reported Gladys Awiti, 53, (pictured) said they never saw her pregnant and believe she could not bear children.But Awiti said, I swear before the living God this child is mine. I cannot steal a baby. I gave birth at my house with my husband by the name of Peter Kimani ... with me while I was still pregnant. She said she gave birth on August 23.